 <span data-ttu-id="8d479-146">如果`alternateChoices`为空数组，此方法不会更新的替代组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8d479-146">If `alternateChoices` is an empty array, this method does not update the set of alternatives.</span></span>  
  
